>>__ Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="hol"};
## `UNCURRY_FORALL_CONV`

``` hol4
PairRules.UNCURRY_FORALL_CONV : conv
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Uncurrys consecutive universal quantifications into a paired universal
quantification.

### Example

``` hol4
>>__ load "PairRules";

>> PairRules.UNCURRY_FORALL_CONV (Term `!x y. x + y = y + x`);

>> PairRules.UNCURRY_FORALL_CONV (Term `!(w,x) (y,z). w+x+y+z = z+y+x+w`);
```

### Failure

`UNCURRY_FORALL_CONV tm` fails if `tm` is not a consecutive universal
quantification.

